{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Base","content":["Preheat oven to 250°F. Grease a springform pan (9 in.) and line bottom and sides with parchment. Place on a baking sheet and set aside.","Place butter into mixing bowl and melt <strong><b>2 min\/212°F\/speed 1<b>.<\/strong> ","Add ginger snaps and sugar and mix <strong><b>5 sec\/speed 7<b>.<\/strong> Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and mix a further <strong><b>10 sec\/speed 7<b><\/strong>.","Spread crumb mixture into base and up sides of prepared springform pan. Press firmly into a compact layer with a spoon or hands. Place in refrigerator while making the filling. Clean mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Filling","content":["Place cream cheese, sour cream, sugar, egg, egg white and vanilla into mixing bowl and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula and mix a further <b>10 sec\/speed 5<b>. Pour ⅔ cream cheese mixture over crust.","Add pumpkin purée, brown sugar and pumpkin spice mix into mixing bowl and mix <b>10 sec\/speed 5<b>.","Drop spoonfuls of pumpkin mixture onto plain mixture and run a knife through batter in a swirling motion to create a marbled effect. Bake 10 minutes (250°F). Reduce temperature to 225°F and bake a further 1 hour 50 minutes (225°F).","Turn off oven, leave door ajar and allow cheesecake to cool 30 minutes before placing in refrigerator to chill completely (approx. 4 hr.). Serve chilled."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Base","content":["4 oz unsalted butter, plus extra to grease","12 oz ginger snap cookies","1 oz sugar"]},{"title":"Filling","content":["16 oz cream cheese, cubed (1 in.)","9 oz sour cream","3 ½ oz sugar","1 large egg","1 egg white, from a large egg","1 tsp vanilla extract","8 oz canned pumpkin purée","2 oz dark brown sugar","1 - 2 tsp homemade pumpkin spice mix"]}],"id":"r254137","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-8K7aBNrx9Kc\/XZWfojv8j8I\/AAAAAAAAfHw\/LuEdEcd0U9YRrNBmQvtOWz7A4wRLz1RKgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_zIeoBgPRztJxsoNf.png","title":"Pumpkin Cheesecake","publishedAt":"2017-10-06T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5 g","fat":"28 g","uom":"per 1 slice","carbohydrates":"41 g","calories":"1812 kJ \/ 433 kcal"},"usefulItems":"parchment paper, springform pan (9 in.), baking sheet, oven, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Serve with fresh whipped cream."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","6h 45m","12 slices"]}